288
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:07,870
healthy and happy

289
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:10,070
forever.

290
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:12,530
Happy New Year.

291
00:19:19,130 --> 00:19:19,950
Excuse me.

292
00:19:20,670 --> 00:19:21,510
Mr. Jiang.

293
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,680
Have a seat.

294
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:28,050
Happy New Year to you.

295
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:35,390
Mr. Du.

296
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,870
Did Du Hanlin wake up?

297
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:40,320
You don’t stay with Du Hanlin at home at New Year’s Eve,

298
00:19:40,330 --> 00:19:42,100
but come here to perform?

299
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:44,640
Thanks for caring about my father.

300
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:48,010
He is very healthy.

301
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,480
And he won’t leave before you.

302
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,120
Also,

303
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:55,810
I didn’t come with them.

304
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,310
After my thing’s done,

305
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:59,320
talk to them.

306
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:20,000
Mr. Jiang.

307
00:20:20,810 --> 00:20:21,250
Mr. Jiang.

308
00:20:22,530 --> 00:20:24,110
At the Opera Association,

309
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,530
you made me really embarrassed.

310
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:27,820
So today

311
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:29,350
I come to argue on it.

312
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:32,080
Let’s talk about the indenture

313
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:33,560
of Shuiyun Theater’s performers.

314
00:20:34,490 --> 00:20:35,040
By the way,

315
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:37,550
I brought you a book.

316
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,040
Have a look.

317
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:45,070
Du Contract Social written by Rousseau.

318
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,150
What?

319
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:47,220
Let me read for you.

320
00:20:47,230 --> 00:20:50,020
This book was written by a French master,

321
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,540
Rousseau.

322
00:20:52,130 --> 00:20:53,050
It’s a good book.

323
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:55,500
In the Chapter 3.

324
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,080
Well.

325
00:20:56,850 --> 00:20:59,130
The social order

326
00:21:00,340 --> 00:21:01,590
should be based on contract

327
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:02,880
instead of force.

328
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:06,940
The most powerful one should turn contract into power,

329
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:08,740
and turn power into service.

330
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:12,740
You don’t understand?

331
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,930
To be precise,

332
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:17,350
you are a powerful man,

333
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:19,580
but you can’t use force...

334
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:21,240
Stop. Stop.

335
00:21:24,120 --> 00:21:24,920
Who are you?

336
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:27,540
I think you are in league

337
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:28,920
with this old guy.

338
00:21:32,170 --> 00:21:32,910
Cut your crap.

339
00:21:33,610 --> 00:21:34,950
I am Du Luobin,

340
00:21:35,210 --> 00:21:37,080
a writer for Shang Xirui.

341
00:21:39,150 --> 00:21:40,140
A well-educated one.

342
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:44,300
You said what we can’t use?

343
00:21:44,310 --> 00:21:46,390
Rousseau said it. We can’t use force.

344
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,790
We can’t use force.

345
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:51,190
Now!

346
00:21:55,870 --> 00:21:56,820
What will you do?

347
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:57,870
-I tell you.
-Dad.

348
00:21:58,290 --> 00:22:00,590
We still need force on something.

349
00:22:00,930 --> 00:22:01,720
But,

350
00:22:02,110 --> 00:22:03,390
the force is not him,

351
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,730
but me.

352
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,500
No, no, no.

353
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:14,570
Take it down. Who are you?

354
00:22:14,580 --> 00:22:15,560
-Why are you here?
-No, no, no.

355
00:22:20,420 --> 00:22:22,020
I forgot to introduce myself.

356
00:22:22,460 --> 00:22:24,260
I am Cao Guixiu.

357
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:25,120
I come

358
00:22:25,130 --> 00:22:28,120
to visit you for Mr. Cheng.

359
00:22:28,350 --> 00:22:30,080
Cheng Fengtai asked you to come?

360
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:30,630
For what?

361
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,470
Stop your nonsense.

362
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,190
No, no, no.

363
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,560
Just tell me

364
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:38,410
whether Shang Xirui did unethical things?

365
00:22:38,950 --> 00:22:40,890
You extort a confession.

366
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:42,330
I’ll sue you.

367
00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:43,570
I ask you again.

368
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:44,900
Did Shang Xirui

369
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:48,050
do unethical things?

370
00:22:56,350 --> 00:22:57,030
Dad.

371
00:23:00,130 --> 00:23:00,960
No.

372
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,380
Speak loudly!

373
00:23:02,970 --> 00:23:04,340
Let everyone hear it.

374
00:23:08,140 --> 00:23:08,830
No.

375
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,460
Who?

376
00:23:16,810 --> 00:23:18,190
Shang Xirui

377
00:23:19,820 --> 00:23:23,320
didn’t do unethical things.

378
00:23:27,740 --> 00:23:28,860
Dad. Dad.

379
00:23:30,020 --> 00:23:30,810
Fine.

380
00:23:32,980 --> 00:23:33,780
Don’t

381
00:23:34,470 --> 00:23:35,930
break your words in future.

382
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:38,290
If you deny it,

383
00:23:38,930 --> 00:23:40,010
I’ll come to you again.

384
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:47,330
Don’t. Don’t.

385
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:52,770
Don’t say you confessed under my force.

386
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:54,730
In Pingyang,

387
00:23:54,740 --> 00:23:55,620
my dad put a gun to

388
00:23:55,630 --> 00:23:57,390
Shang Xirui’s head

389
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:59,820
and let him choose one between life and opera.

390
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:02,350
He chose opera.

391
00:24:05,810 --> 00:24:06,600
No, no.

392
00:24:06,610 --> 00:24:09,470
People changing views according to circumstances like you

393
00:24:09,610 --> 00:24:11,870
-Dad.
-deserve to frame Shang Xirui?

394
00:24:15,710 --> 00:24:16,790
Don’t forget

395
00:24:17,490 --> 00:24:18,530
what I said today.

396
00:24:19,890 --> 00:24:20,460
Dad!

397
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:21,850
Dad!

398
00:24:23,090 --> 00:24:24,170
Are you okay? Dad.

399
00:24:24,410 --> 00:24:25,330
-Dad.
-Go.

400
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:26,080
Mr. Jiang.

401
00:24:26,090 --> 00:24:27,530
I don’t think this book is useful to you.

402
00:24:31,580 --> 00:24:33,250
Mr. Jiang. Mr. Jiang. Mr. Jiang.

403
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:33,980
Are you all right?

404
00:24:33,990 --> 00:24:34,520
Dad,

405
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:36,620
let’s sue him.

406
00:24:37,450 --> 00:24:38,700
Nonsense.

407
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:41,940
Who did he say he is?

408
00:24:41,950 --> 00:24:43,070
Cao Guixiu.

409
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:44,970
His father is Commander Cao.

410
00:24:45,210 --> 00:24:46,850
Once you sue him,

411
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:48,920
you’ll lose your life.

412
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:51,110
So we just submit to humiliation

413
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,350
on the New Year’s Eve?

414
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:54,530
We can’t.

415
00:24:57,290 --> 00:24:59,080
Shang Xirui.

416
00:25:00,010 --> 00:25:01,390
I’ll see

417
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:06,070
how long Cheng Fengtai can protect you?

418
00:25:11,850 --> 00:25:12,780
Uncle.

419
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:16,510
Tell me if you have

420
00:25:17,030 --> 00:25:18,240
such a good thing.

421
00:25:19,370 --> 00:25:21,980
Even if Shang Xirui was a cannibal,

422
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:23,820
I could solve the problem for you.

423
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:25,670
There’s no one

424
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:27,740
who I can’t deal with in Peking.

425
00:25:30,850 --> 00:25:31,690
Mr. Shang

426
00:25:32,530 --> 00:25:34,040
doesn’t have such a good appetite.

427
00:25:34,990 --> 00:25:36,270
But no matter what,

428
00:25:37,970 --> 00:25:41,080
I really appreciate your kindness.

429
00:25:44,930 --> 00:25:45,910
Uncle.

430
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:49,100
I helped you on two big things.

431
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:50,470
You just appreciate me in words?

432
00:25:59,080 --> 00:26:00,500
I care you just like

433
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:03,430
I care Mr. Shang.

434
00:26:05,730 --> 00:26:07,970
I’ll pay your soldiers’ salary this year.

435
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:17,250
Uncle, play possum?

436
00:26:23,950 --> 00:26:24,600
Madam!

437
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:28,590
What did you want to tell uncle?

438
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:35,670
Be good. It’s all right.

439
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,480
Fengtai.

440
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:38,470
Come with me.

441
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:47,520
I agreed with Cao Guixiu

442
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,070
that you give him firearms

443
00:26:50,570 --> 00:26:52,080
as long as he saved you out.

444
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,360
You did it in haste.

445
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:03,920
You shouldn’t have promised him.

446
00:27:06,340 --> 00:27:07,780
I saved you,

447
00:27:09,050 --> 00:27:10,360
but you are blaming me?

448
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:13,950
I know you worried about me.

449
00:27:16,290 --> 00:27:17,060
But

450
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:21,210
you’ve put me in dilemma.

451
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,850
Don’t worry.

452
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:28,160
Just help him.

453
00:27:28,610 --> 00:27:29,750
I’ll speak for you

454
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,080
to Commander Cao.

455
00:27:31,420 --> 00:27:32,850
They are father and son.

456
00:27:33,450 --> 00:27:35,160
So they can’t be enemies.

457
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,090
I don’t fear that Commander Cao knows it.

458
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,270
What do you fear?

459
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:47,590
You fear that Cao Guixiu doesn’t give you money?

460
00:27:48,170 --> 00:27:50,830
Rest assured. He has money.

461
00:27:51,690 --> 00:27:53,010
I fear nothing.

462
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:56,770
I just don’t want to be close to Cao Guixiu.

463
00:27:58,090 --> 00:28:00,270
You don’t need to do business with him for your life.

464
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:02,110
Only once or twice.

465
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,750
Refuse him with some reasons

466
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:04,740
in future.

467
00:28:11,310 --> 00:28:13,700
You don’t even listen to me?

468
00:28:17,430 --> 00:28:18,080
Meixin.

469
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:21,830
Cao Guixiu said that

470
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:24,560
Commander Cao pretends to support the northeast

471
00:28:25,130 --> 00:28:27,990
and is in league with Japanese in fact.

472
00:28:28,850 --> 00:28:31,150
He said he’s the one who’s really anti-Japanese.

473
00:28:32,050 --> 00:28:33,270
Of course I don’t believe him

474
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,580
without any evidence.

475
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:37,040
But he must have evil intentions

476
00:28:38,270 --> 00:28:39,830
to say such words.

477
00:28:40,870 --> 00:28:41,990
Meixin,

478
00:28:42,170 --> 00:28:44,450
how do I dare be close with him?

479
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,110
What does he want?

480
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,350
How can he frame his dad?

481
00:29:04,630 --> 00:29:05,870
Madam,

482
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,750
did you persuade Cheng Fengtai?

483
00:29:15,210 --> 00:29:16,130
Cao Guixiu,

484
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,380
you hate that I married your dad

485
00:29:20,230 --> 00:29:22,710
and always oppose him.

486
00:29:23,670 --> 00:29:24,910
Commander Cao ignored

487
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,390
the little things.

488
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:29,920
But now, you said that he does business with Japanese.

489
00:29:30,570 --> 00:29:33,760
How come you framed him of this?

490
00:29:36,130 --> 00:29:37,990
I framed my dad of this?

491
00:29:40,310 --> 00:29:41,270
Cheng Meixin.

492
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,970
Who do you think you are?

493
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:48,360
And who do you think I am?

494
00:29:50,050 --> 00:29:51,040
Who are you?

495
00:29:52,140 --> 00:29:56,250
The one who protects our country.

496
00:29:58,730 --> 00:30:01,020
You? Who believes it?

497
00:30:03,450 --> 00:30:04,920
I’ll make you believe.

498
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:22,150
You must be tired lately.

499
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:26,150
Look, you lost weight.

500
00:30:26,950 --> 00:30:28,590
But you look more beautiful.

501
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:30,190
No.

502
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:33,970
Nothing changed.

503
00:30:34,220 --> 00:30:35,590
Your son and I lived well.

504
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,360
I also think so.

505
00:30:40,090 --> 00:30:41,730
You turn your back on me now.

506
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,380
I should have

507
00:30:43,390 --> 00:30:44,870
died in Laozi Ridge.

508
00:30:44,990 --> 00:30:45,790
Don’t.

509
00:30:46,150 --> 00:30:47,270
You should come back.

510
00:30:47,670 --> 00:30:49,110
You need to go to the theater.

511
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,290
That’s your business.

512
00:30:52,060 --> 00:30:52,720
I don’t go.

513
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:55,210
There is full of the sounds of musical instruments

514
00:30:55,950 --> 00:30:57,360
Their voice is even louder

515
00:30:57,370 --> 00:30:59,180
than bugles of Commander Cao.

516
00:30:59,190 --> 00:31:00,160
I’m not willing to go.

517
00:31:01,180 --> 00:31:02,400
Look at you.

518
00:31:04,130 --> 00:31:05,600
Darling.

519
00:31:06,730 --> 00:31:08,240
Xiang’er.

520
00:31:09,630 --> 00:31:10,810
There’s no regret

521
00:31:11,940 --> 00:31:12,970
after you decide something.

522
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:14,900
The business of Shuiyun Theater is a dream of mine.

523
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:16,300
Please.

524
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:20,190
Mr. Cheng.

525
00:31:20,770 --> 00:31:22,070
The freight agent has something urgent.

526
00:31:24,710 --> 00:31:25,430
Something urgent?

527
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:28,470
How urgent is it?

528
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,880
Mr. Ma is worried to death.

529
00:31:29,890 --> 00:31:31,110
He said the Mr. Cao came.

530
00:31:32,390 --> 00:31:33,750
We just finished the dinner.

531
00:31:34,210 --> 00:31:36,290
Cao Guixiu comes to make trouble.

532
00:31:37,670 --> 00:31:40,930
Can he stop tonight?

533
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:45,210
Have a sleep. I’ll be back later.

534
00:31:55,710 --> 00:31:56,350
Wait for me.

535
00:32:03,410 --> 00:32:04,820
What’s the matter, Mr. Cao?

536
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:06,080
You asked me out

537
00:32:06,090 --> 00:32:07,750
on such a cold evening.

538
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:10,410
Nothing special.

539
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:12,750
I’m worried that you are

540
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,660
unsatisfied with my two gifts.

541
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:16,580
So I prepared the third one.

542
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:22,910
You let your man surround my storage just to give me a gift.

543
00:32:23,650 --> 00:32:25,380
I don’t deserve this.

544
00:32:25,390 --> 00:32:26,710
Don’t say that

545
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:28,770
until you see it.

546
00:32:48,950 --> 00:32:51,500
A Japanese gun.

547
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:53,220
Where is it from?

548
00:32:54,980 --> 00:32:55,630
Have a guess.

549
00:32:59,530 --> 00:33:01,970
I heard that the bandits in the north are savage.

550
00:33:02,970 --> 00:33:05,180
They even dare to rob Japanese soldiers.

551
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:09,890
You did it?

552
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:23,100
How wise you are.

553
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,560
This is a booty

554
00:33:27,270 --> 00:33:28,440
or an evidence?

555
00:33:30,010 --> 00:33:31,210
If you believe me,

556
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:33,270
take it as an evidence.

557
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:40,210
I only believe that you fight against Japanese.

558
00:33:43,910 --> 00:33:44,770
That’s enough.

559
00:33:45,370 --> 00:33:46,370
I’ll prove the rest

560
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:49,630
when there’s a chance.

561
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:54,100
As long as you take me as your friend.

562
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:57,270
We are more than friends.

563
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:58,750
We ate dinner

564
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:01,130
on the New Years’ Eve.

565
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,360
What a comfortable sentence.

566
00:34:23,210 --> 00:34:23,860
Mr. Shang.

567
00:34:25,199 --> 00:34:26,350
Mr. Shang, did you hear that?

568
00:34:27,030 --> 00:34:28,909
Liu Hanyun asked me to perform at his mansion.

569
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:31,690
Who is Liu Hanyun?

570
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:34,449
You don’t know him?

571
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:37,610
He is only second to the chairman in Nanking.

572
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:40,130
He’s just an official.

573
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:42,250
Are you so happy just for performing for an official?

574
00:34:43,170 --> 00:34:44,520
You know nothing.

575
00:34:44,929 --> 00:34:46,420
Liu Hanyun knows opera well.

576
00:34:46,429 --> 00:34:48,330
He watched many good performances.

577
